Problem: DSO tools like GitLab, AAP, SonarQube, artifact repositories, container registries, databases, execution nodes, or test automation services fail and require manual troubleshooting.

Telemetry: Prometheus service metrics, Nagios service checks, Splunk logs, application health endpoints.

AAP remediation: Restart approved services, validate dependencies, check disk/memory/connectivity, collect diagnostics, escalate after repeated failure instead of looping.

Savings: Faster recovery of shared DSO platforms and less repetitive admin effort.

